msgstr "Cloud API 錯誤：%s"

msgid "Cloud API test succeeded! Result: %s"
msgstr "Cloud API 測試成功！翻譯結果：%s"

msgid "Comments are now fully locked down across the entire site."
msgstr "目前全站留言功能已被徹底鎖定。"

msgid "Comments Control"
msgstr "留言功能控制"

msgid "Completely Disable Comments"
msgstr "完全禁用留言功能"

msgid "Completely removes the `post_tag` entries from the native WordPress sitemap while keeping the main post and author listings for a leaner sitemap."
msgstr "從 WP 原生 Sitemap 結構中徹底拔除 `post_tag` 項目，保留主要文章與作者目錄，精簡 Sitemap 指向。"

msgid "Completely Turn Off Site Comments"
msgstr "完全關閉網站留言功能"

msgid "Connection error. Please try again."
msgstr "連線錯誤，請重試。"

msgid "Copy failed. Please select the table manually and copy it."
msgstr "複製失敗，請手動選取表格複製。"

msgid "Copy to Clipboard (Paste into Sheets/Excel)"
msgstr "一鍵複製到剪貼簿 (貼上 Sheets/Excel)"

msgid "Could not retrieve a translation. Please check that the API key is correct."
msgstr "無法取得翻譯結果，請檢查 API Key 是否正確"

msgid "Custom Robots Meta"
msgstr "自訂 Robots Meta"

msgid "Custom size: %s"
msgstr "自訂尺寸：%s"

msgid "Data Preview"
msgstr "數據預覽"

msgid "Date"
msgstr "日期"

msgid "Default Social Share Image (og:image)"
msgstr "預設社群分享圖 (og:image)"

msgid "Defaults to <code>views</code> (used by WP-PostViews). Enter the view count custom field name (meta key) used on your site."
msgstr "預設為 <code>views</code> (WP-PostViews 用)。請輸入您網站使用的瀏覽量自訂欄位名稱 (Meta Key)。"

msgid "Disable Generation"
msgstr "停用生成"

msgid "Disable Non-Essential RSS Feeds"
msgstr "停用非必要 RSS 訂閱源"

msgid "Disable specific thumbnail sizes to keep a single upload from generating dozens of unused copies that eat up your hosting disk space."
msgstr "自訂停用特定寬高的圖片縮圖規格，防止上傳一張圖片生成數十個無用分身佔用虛擬主機硬碟容量。"

msgid "Disabled thumbnail settings only affect newly uploaded images. To free up disk space, use the tool below to batch delete thumbnail files already generated for existing images."
msgstr "已停用的縮圖設定僅對「新上傳」圖片有效。若要釋放硬碟空間，可使用下方工具批次刪除歷史圖片已產生的縮圖檔案。"

msgid "Do Not Track Logged-In Administrators and Editors"
msgstr "不追蹤登入中的管理員與編輯"

msgid "Download CSV File (Excel)"
msgstr "下載 CSV 檔案 (Excel)"

msgid "e.g. 123456789012345"
msgstr "例如：123456789012345"

msgid "e.g. yBlog"
msgstr "例如：yBlog"

msgid "e.g. yBlog shares website building tutorials, software reviews, and everyday notes, offering practical guides and hands-on webmaster experience."
msgstr "例如：yBlog 分享網站架設教學、軟體工具評測與生活記事，提供實用的教學筆記與站長經驗談。"

msgid "Enable Advanced Event Tracking"
msgstr "啟用進階事件追蹤"

msgid "Enable Homepage Meta Tags"
msgstr "啟用首頁 Meta 標籤"

msgid "Enable Meta Pixel Tracking"
msgstr "啟用 Meta Pixel 追蹤"

msgid "Enter a Cloud Translation API key created in the Google Cloud console (<a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">how to get an API key</a>).<br/><strong>Fallback (no key required)</strong>: leave this field empty and the plugin automatically falls back to the keyless public Google Translate endpoint.<br/><strong>An API key is recommended</strong>: the keyless endpoint often produces lower-quality slugs (e.g. <code>how-was-it-able-9</code>), while the official Cloud API returns noticeably more accurate translations and includes a monthly free quota."
msgstr "請輸入於 Google Cloud 主控台建立的 Cloud Translation API 金鑰（<a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">如何申請 API 金鑰</a>）。<br/><strong>免金鑰備援</strong>：此欄留空時，系統會自動改用免金鑰的 Google Translate 公開端點。<br/><strong>建議使用 API 金鑰</strong>：免金鑰端點翻譯品質較差，可能產生如 <code>how-was-it-able-9</code> 的網址字串；官方 Cloud API 翻譯明顯較精準，且每月提供免費額度。"

msgid "Enter a numbers-only Meta Pixel ID"
msgstr "請輸入純數字的 Meta Pixel ID"

msgid "Enter your Meta (Facebook) Pixel ID (numbers only). You can find it on the settings page of Facebook Events Manager."
msgstr "請輸入您的 Meta (Facebook) 像素編號（純數字）。可在 Facebook 事件管理工具的設定頁中找到。"

msgid "Exclude Site Staff"
msgstr "排除網站管理人員"

msgid "Failed to load the media library. Please paste the image URL directly."
msgstr "媒體庫載入失敗，請直接貼上圖片網址。"

msgid "Failed to load: %1$s"
msgstr "載入失敗：%1$s"

msgid "Filter published posts by month and export their dates, titles, category and tag topics, permalinks, and view count statistics."
msgstr "篩選指定月份的發布文章，匯出包含日期、標題、分類與標籤主題、網址連結、以及瀏覽量統計數據。"

msgid "Fixes the white background of JavaScript-rendered GitHub Gist table blocks so they blend into dark themes."
msgstr "解決 JavaScript 產生的 GitHub Gist 表格區塊出現白色背景的問題，使其融入深色主題。"

msgid "Force GitHub Gist Code Blocks into Dark Mode"
msgstr "強制將 GitHub Gist 程式碼區塊轉換為深色模式"

msgid "Full cleanup: deletes every thumbnail of each image (e.g. 150x150, 300x300), which may cause 404 broken images on the front end or slow pages that have to load the original image."
msgstr "完整清除：將刪除該圖片的所有縮圖（例如 150x150, 300x300 等），前端頁面可能會因找不到圖片而回傳 404 破圖或需加載原圖而變慢。"

msgid "GitHub Gist Dark Mode Fix"
msgstr "GitHub Gist 程式碼深色修正"

msgid "Global Comment Blocking Switch"
msgstr "留言全局封鎖開關"

msgid "Helps Google display the correct <strong>site name</strong> (instead of the domain name) and site logo in search results (the Site Icon is used first, falling back to the share image above when not set). Requires \"Enable Homepage Meta Tags\" above to be turned on as well."
msgstr "協助 Google 在搜尋結果顯示正確的<strong>站名</strong>（而非網域名稱）與網站 logo（優先使用「網站圖示 Site Icon」，未設定時退回上方分享圖）。需同時開啟上方「啟用首頁 Meta 標籤」。"

msgid "Homepage Meta Description"
msgstr "首頁 Meta Description"

msgid "Homepage Meta Tags & Structured Data"
msgstr "首頁 Meta 標籤與結構化資料"

msgid "If enabling \"Clean Up HTML Head\" previously turned your embed cards into plain links, then after <strong>turning \"Clean Up HTML Head\" off</strong> you need to click this button to clear the failed oEmbed cache from the database so post pages can re-fetch and restore the rich preview cards."
msgstr "若您先前啟用過「清理 HTML Head」導致嵌入卡片變成普通連結，在<strong>關閉「清理 HTML Head」</strong>後，您需要點擊此按鈕清除資料庫中的 oEmbed 失敗快取，文章頁面才會重新抓取並還原精美的預覽卡片。"

msgid "If you still use Jetpack or a legacy offline editor that relies on XML-RPC, do not enable this option."
msgstr "若您仍在使用 Jetpack 或依賴 XML-RPC 的舊版離線編輯器，請勿啟用此選項。"

msgid "In addition to the base <code>PageView</code>, the system automatically sends the following standard events on the appropriate pages for advanced ad audience optimization:"
msgstr "除了基礎的 <code>PageView</code> 外，系統會自動在適當的頁面發送以下標準事件以做進階廣告受眾優化："

msgid "Insufficient permissions"
msgstr "權限不足"

msgid "Insufficient permissions."
msgstr "權限不足"

msgid "Integrates the Meta (Facebook) Pixel tracking code, automatically loading the base PageView event plus advanced marketing tracking events on the front end to improve ad conversion rates and audience optimization accuracy."
msgstr "整合 Meta (Facebook) Pixel 追蹤代碼，在網站前端自動載入基礎 PageView 及進階行銷追蹤事件，提升廣告轉換率與受眾優化精準度。"

msgid "Invalid month format."
msgstr "月份格式錯誤。"

msgid "Invalid security check (nonce validation failed)"
msgstr "無效的安全性權限檢查 (Nonce validation failed)"

