msgstr "免金鑰 API 測試連線失敗：%s"

msgid "Keyless translation test succeeded! Result: %s"
msgstr "免金鑰翻譯測試成功！翻譯結果：%s"

msgid "Large"
msgstr "大尺寸 (Large)"

msgid "Link"
msgstr "連結"

msgid "Load the Meta Pixel Tracking Code on the Front End"
msgstr "開啟前端 Meta Pixel 追蹤碼載入"

msgid "Loading post data, please wait..."
msgstr "正在讀取文章數據，請稍後..."

msgid "Manage your WordPress site optimization and SEO essentials in one place, including comment control, thumbnail optimization, and slug translation."
msgstr "一站式管理您的 WordPress 網站優化與 SEO 基礎配置，整合留言防制、縮圖最佳化與網址翻譯。"

msgid "Marks tag archives, date archives, internal search pages, and deep post pagination (page 3 and beyond) as `noindex, follow` to focus crawl priority and keep the site from generating large amounts of low-quality or duplicate content."
msgstr "將標籤存檔頁、日期封存頁、內部搜尋頁與第 3 頁以上的深層文章分頁，標記為 `noindex, follow`，聚焦爬蟲權重，避免網站產生大量低質量或重複內容。"

msgid "Maximum number of characters for generated English slugs (30 to 50 recommended). The system automatically reserves 12 characters for appending the post ID as duplicate protection."
msgstr "產生的英文網址最大字元數（建議為 30 至 50 之間）。系統會自動預留 12 個字元供後續追加文章 ID 做防重複保護。"

msgid "Maximum Slug Length"
msgstr "最大字元長度"

