msgstr "Omni 站長工具與 SEO 設定"

msgid "One-Click oEmbed Cache Clearing"
msgstr "一鍵清除 oEmbed 快取"

msgid "Only clean the thumbnail sizes checked as disabled (recommended)"
msgstr "僅清理已勾選停用的縮圖尺寸 (推薦)"

msgid "Only the homepage, category, and author RSS feeds are kept; all other unused feeds return a 410 response to stop crawlers from putting useless request load on your server."
msgstr "僅放行首頁、文章分類與作者的 RSS Feed，阻斷其他無用 RSS 訂閱（回傳 410）以防止爬蟲對伺服器造成無效請求負荷。"

msgid "Optimize HTML head tags, manage RSS feed sources, and clean up the sitemap to prevent unnecessary exposure of your site structure."
msgstr "優化 HTML 頭部標籤，管理 RSS 訂閱來源並清洗 Sitemap 以防網站結構不必要地暴露。"

msgid "Output Meta Description and Open Graph Tags on the Homepage"
msgstr "於首頁輸出 Meta Description 與 Open Graph 標籤"

msgid "Output only on the first page of the homepage (not repeated on paginated pages), including <code>description</code>, <code>og:title</code>, <code>og:description</code>, <code>og:url</code>, <code>og:image</code>, <code>og:locale</code>, and <code>twitter:card</code>."
msgstr "僅在首頁第一頁輸出（分頁不重複），包含 <code>description</code>、<code>og:title</code>、<code>og:description</code>、<code>og:url</code>、<code>og:image</code>、<code>og:locale</code> 與 <code>twitter:card</code>。"

msgid "Output WebSite and Organization JSON-LD"
msgstr "輸出 WebSite 與 Organization JSON-LD"

msgid "Please enter an API key first."
msgstr "請先輸入 API 金鑰。"

msgid "Please select a month to export."
msgstr "請選擇要匯出的月份。"

msgid "Please specify a month to export."
msgstr "請指定要匯出的月份。"

msgid "Post data copied to clipboard! You can paste it directly into Google Sheets or Excel."
msgstr "文章數據已複製到剪貼簿！可直接貼上至 Google 試算表或 Excel 中。"

msgid "Post Data Export"
msgstr "文章數據匯出"

msgid "Post Title"
msgstr "文章標題"

