msgstr "即時預覽數據"

msgid "Recommended length is 90 to 160 characters; longer descriptions get truncated in search results. Current count:"
msgstr "建議 90 至 160 個字元，過長會在搜尋結果中被截斷。目前字數："

msgid "Remove All WordPress XML-RPC Methods"
msgstr "移除所有 WordPress XML-RPC 方法"

msgid "Remove Redundant HTML Tags"
msgstr "移除 HTML 多餘標籤"

msgid "Remove Tags from the Sitemap"
msgstr "從網站地圖中移除標籤 (Tags)"

msgid "Removes all WordPress methods from <code>xmlrpc.php</code> (<code>wp.*</code>, <code>metaWeblog.*</code>, <code>pingback.*</code>, and so on), keeping only three harmless system methods. This blocks the <strong>brute-force</strong> and pingback abuse attack surface that bypasses login page protection, and also removes the <code>X-Pingback</code> response header. It does not rely on .htaccess and is compatible with any server."
msgstr "清除 <code>xmlrpc.php</code> 中全部 WordPress 方法（<code>wp.*</code>、<code>metaWeblog.*</code>、<code>pingback.*</code> 等），僅保留三個無害的系統方法，阻斷繞過登入頁防護的<strong>暴力破解</strong>與 pingback 濫用攻擊面，同時移除 <code>X-Pingback</code> 回應標頭。不依賴 .htaccess，相容任何伺服器。"

msgid "Removes redundant feed links and REST API markup from the `<head>` section, keeping your source code clean and improving privacy."
msgstr "移除 `<head>` 中冗餘的 Feed 連結與 REST API 頭部標記，保持源碼乾淨度並增強隱私。"

msgid "Reset Site-Wide Embed Preview Cards"
msgstr "重設全站嵌入預覽卡片"

msgid "Safe mode: only deletes the sizes you checked as disabled above, keeping every other thumbnail size intact to avoid broken images on the front end."
msgstr "安全模式：只會刪除您上方勾選停用的尺寸，保留其他正常的縮圖尺寸，避免前端文章破圖。"

msgid "Save Changes"
msgstr "儲存變更"

msgid "Scanning media library image attachments and starting cleanup (mode: %1$s)..."
msgstr "開始掃描媒體庫圖片附件並進行清理（模式：%1$s）..."

msgid "Schema.org Structured Data"
msgstr "Schema.org 結構化資料"

msgid "Security check failed. Please try again."
msgstr "安全性檢查失敗，請重新操作。"

msgid "Select a social share image (1200 × 630 recommended)"
msgstr "選擇社群分享圖（建議 1200 × 630）"

msgid "Select Export Month"
msgstr "選擇匯出月份"

msgid "Select from Media Library"
msgstr "從媒體庫選取"

msgid "Select Thumbnail Sizes to Disable"
msgstr "選擇要停用的縮圖尺寸"

