msgstr "SEO 優化與 HTML 清理"

msgid "Server returned an error: %1$s"
msgstr "伺服器回傳失敗：%1$s"

msgid "Set noindex on Search, Tag, and Paginated Pages"
msgstr "搜尋、標籤與分頁設定 noindex"

msgid "Settings"
msgstr "設定"

msgid "Site Name Abbreviation (alternateName)"
msgstr "站名簡稱 (alternateName)"

msgid "Site-wide oEmbed cache cleared successfully (%d cache records deleted). Refresh your pages to see the result."
msgstr "成功清除全站 oEmbed 快取（共刪除 %d 筆快取紀錄）。請重新整理網頁查看效果。"

msgid "Slug Translator"
msgstr "中英網址翻譯"

msgid "Start Batch Cleanup"
msgstr "開始進行批次清理"

msgid "Test API Key Connection"
msgstr "測試 API 金鑰連線"

msgid "Testing connection..."
msgstr "測試連線中..."

msgid "The \"%s\" plugin was detected. To avoid conflicts from duplicate meta tag output, the settings in this section are kept but <strong>front-end output is automatically disabled</strong> until that plugin is deactivated."
msgstr "偵測到「%s」外掛。為避免重複輸出 meta 標籤造成衝突，本區設定將保留但<strong>自動停止前台輸出</strong>，直到該外掛停用為止。"

msgid "The keyless translation endpoint returned unexpected data."
msgstr "免金鑰翻譯端點回傳異常資料"

msgid "The preview image shown when your homepage is shared on Facebook, LINE, or Telegram. Recommended size: <strong>1200 × 630</strong> pixels. If left empty, social platforms will pick an image on their own (possibly an author avatar or a random image)."
msgstr "FB / LINE / Telegram 分享首頁時顯示的預覽圖，建議尺寸 <strong>1200 × 630</strong> 像素。留空時社群平台將自行抓圖（可能抓到作者頭像或隨機圖片）。"

msgid "This scans every image attachment in the media library and removes the corresponding thumbnail files (original full-size images are kept). This is a destructive action; back up your site first."
msgstr "這將掃描媒體庫中所有的圖片附件，並移除對應的縮圖實體檔案（保留原始大圖）。此為破壞性動作，建議先進行網站備份。"

msgid "Thumbnail"
msgstr "縮圖 (Thumbnail)"

msgid "Use this image"
msgstr "使用這張圖片"

msgid "View Count Custom Field (Meta Key)"
msgstr "瀏覽量自訂欄位 (Meta Key)"

msgid "View Post"
msgstr "查看文章"

msgid "Views"
msgstr "瀏覽量"

msgid "When enabled, logged-in users with post editing capability (<code>edit_posts</code>) will not load the Pixel tracking code when browsing the front end, keeping staff browsing behavior from polluting your ad audiences and conversion data (recommended to keep on)."
msgstr "啟用後，具備文章編輯權限（<code>edit_posts</code>）的登入使用者瀏覽前台時將不會載入 Pixel 追蹤碼，避免站方人員自身的瀏覽行為污染廣告受眾與轉換數據（建議保持開啟）。"

msgid "When enabled, the Meta Pixel tracking script is inserted into the `<head>` section of every public front-end page and the base <code>PageView</code> event fires automatically."
msgstr "啟用後會在網站所有公開前端頁面的 `<head>` 區域插入 Meta Pixel 追蹤腳本，並自動觸發基礎的 <code>PageView</code> 事件。"

msgid "When enabled, this turns off comment and trackback support for all post types, hides existing comments, closes comments on new posts, and hides the admin comments menu and the dashboard comments widget."
msgstr "啟用後會關閉所有文章類型的留言及跟蹤支援、隱藏現有留言、關閉新文章留言入口、並隱藏後台留言選單與儀表板上的留言小工具。"

msgid "When no full-featured SEO plugin is installed, outputs a meta description, Open Graph social sharing tags, and Schema.org (WebSite / Organization) structured data on the homepage. OG tags for single posts are left to your theme; this section only affects the homepage."
msgstr "在未安裝大型 SEO 外掛時，於首頁輸出 Meta Description、Open Graph 社群分享標籤與 Schema.org（WebSite / Organization）結構化資料。單篇文章頁的 OG 標籤請交由佈景主題處理，本區僅作用於首頁。"

msgid "When you publish or save a post with an Asian-language title (Chinese, Japanese, Korean, Thai, etc.), the title is automatically translated into a clean English URL slug via the Google Translate API, improving SEO friendliness and preventing garbled characters when non-Latin URLs are copied."
msgstr "當發布或儲存含亞洲語言（中、日、韓、泰文等）標題的文章時，自動呼叫 Google 翻譯 API 翻譯為英文 URL Slug，增強 SEO 搜尋友好度，並避免非拉丁字母網址複製時產生亂碼。"

msgid "WP Embed Block Dark Mode Fix (Embed Card)"
msgstr "WP 嵌入區塊深色修正 (Embed Card)"

msgid "XML-RPC Security Hardening"
msgstr "XML-RPC 安全強化"

